<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.1.5">
<l>āṅku māvali vēḷviyi lirantuceṉ ṟakaliṭa maḷantāyar</l>
<l>pūṅko ṭikkiṉa viṭaiporu tavaṉiṭam poṉmalar tikaḻvēṅkai</l>
<l>kōṅku ceṇpakak kompiṉil kutikoṭu kurakkiṉa miraittōṭi</l>
<l>tēṉka lantataṇ palaṅkaṉi nukartaru tiruvayin tirapuramē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of him who fought the bull of the herd</l>
<l rend="indent">for the herders’ blossoming creeper[-like girl],</l>
<l>Having measured the wide space [of earth]</l>
<l rend="indent">having gone begging in Māvali’s sacrifice that day,</l>
<l>Is Tiruvayintirapuram where monkey troops,</l>
<l rend="indent">which grab and leap on branches</l>
<l>Of champaka, silk-cotton, and vēnkai with golden blossoms shining,</l>
<l rend="indent">running [and] panting, naturally relish cool jackfruit full of nectar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
